00:01.190 --> 00:02.910
Previously on damages:

00:02.930 --> 00:04.400
Patty's talked a lot about her son,

00:04.440 --> 00:06.760
but she's never once
mentioned who his father is.

00:06.790 --> 00:09.160
So,you think he's purcell's kid?

00:09.180 --> 00:10.560
I always wanted a son.

00:10.590 --> 00:12.800
I just didn't know I actually had one.

00:12.830 --> 00:15.410
You were found with your wife's body.

00:15.430 --> 00:17.640
There's no sign of forced entry.

00:17.660 --> 00:20.250
Her ring. She's not wearing it.

00:20.260 --> 00:23.510
You find that ring,and
you find my wife's killer.

00:23.890 --> 00:26.550
