daniel killed his wife,

00:26.570 --> 00:31.490
but his consulting firm has worked
for unr for more than a decade.

00:31.500 --> 00:33.430
Whatever you dragged our company into,

00:33.470 --> 00:36.200
it better not involve anything other
than retrieving stolen documents.

00:36.230 --> 00:40.090
This company is killing people,and
that's the guy who calls the shots.

00:40.120 --> 00:42.450
Walter kendrick,ceo.

00:42.480 --> 00:46.730
Unr is making record profits
using toxic chemicals.

00:46.740 --> 00:49.570
There's a reporter you need to meet.

00:49.600 --> 00:52.200
Josh reston. Do you mind me
asking where you get your water?

00:52.210 --> 00:54.810
Do you think it's contaminated
from the coal plant?

00:54.840 --> 00:57.110
Ultima national is bulletproof.

00:57.130 --> 00:59.770
Represent me,and I'll
tell you everything.

