- Christine!

02:26.350 --> 02:28.550
You're missing all the fun.

02:28.560 --> 02:31.350
Danny,please. Daniel... daniel!

02:31.360 --> 02:33.590
- You're missing all the fun.
- Christine!

02:33.600 --> 02:35.260
Daniel,daniel...

02:35.270 --> 02:40.070
Purcell. Purcell,let's go.

02:43.070 --> 02:47.500
Daniel purcell told me about
a reporter in west virginia.

02:47.520 --> 02:49.600
Now that he's in jail,he's
suddenly cooperating?

02:49.630 --> 02:52.380
Yeah,being framed for his
wife's murder changed his mind.

02:52.400 --> 02:53.710
What's the reporter's name?

02:53.720 --> 02:55.910
Josh reston.

02:55.920 --> 02:57.200
This is what I have on him.

02:57.220 --> 03:01.010
He thinks that ultima national resources
is poisoning people with aracite.

03:01.020 --> 03:03.090
Unfortunately,we can't find him.

03:03.100 --> 03:05.010
You think ultima national got to him?

03:05.030 --> 03:06.920
I don't know...

03:06.940 --> 03:09.390
but tom's arranging for
travel down to west virginia.

03:09.410 --> 03:12.520
You both leave for
the airport in an hour.

03:13.100 --> 03:17.110
Patty,we still haven't proven
that unr killed purcell's wife.

03:17.130 --> 03:19.530
I'd rather stay here and work on that.

03:19.570 --> 03:23.160
If we're going after ultima
national,we need josh reston.

03:23.180 --> 03:25.930
You and tom are going to find him.

03:26.640 --> 03:28.780
I'll pack a bag.

03:29.300 --> 03:31.510
And ellen...

03:31.520 --> 03:36.040
the next time I give you an assignment,just
nod your head and get it done.

